title: Mass Effect 1 - DLC Pack v2
description:
== Description ==
This DLC Pack includes both Mass Effect 1 DLCs - Bring Down the Sky and Pinnacle Station.
Also included are patches needed to run new content, updating the game to the newest version available.
And as if that wasn't enough of goodness, everything comes with a neat installer, that does most of the job.

This installer does not require any serial keys for DLCs or separate cracks.
Everything is bundled and automated - just install it and play.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
